query:
SELECT
                        st.trip_id,
                        st.stop_id,
                        st.arrival,
                        st.departure
                    FROM
                        stop_time st
                    WHERE
                        st.arrival BETWEEN $1 AND ($1 + INTERVAL '4 hours')
                        AND st.trip_id IN (
                            SELECT
                                t.id
                            FROM
                                trip t
                            WHERE
                                t.assigned IS NOT NULL
                        )
                    ORDER BY
                        st.arrival
